  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848390/extras/505c80aa840052f9716b4370cbd11d36.avif?t=1694457814\" width=500 height=123 /></span><br><br><strong> ◦ Resources management</strong><br>In Kings&Cities, resources are represented by gauges. Make your choices wisely, because if one of them falls to 0, it is the end of your leadership on Epeiros. <br><br><strong> ◦ Leader's quests</strong><br>During your games, the ruler of your kingdom will send you quests. Complete them to obtain favors.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848390/extras/d0a5d08e8586337d8cb484ccbe93fd8d.poster.avif?t=1694457814\" width=500 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848390/extras/d0a5d08e8586337d8cb484ccbe93fd8d.webm?t=1694457814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848390/extras/d0a5d08e8586337d8cb484ccbe93fd8d.mp4?t=1694457814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong> ◦ Diplomacy</strong><br>Relations with other kingdoms and empires fluctuate depending on your actions. Find powerful allies to help you but beware! Times are hard and betrayals are common.<br><br><strong> ◦ Cultures & Religions</strong><br>The factions of Kings&Cities are separated into 5 cultures and 6 religions offering great replayability.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848390/extras/505c80aa840052f9716b4370cbd11d36.avif?t=1694457814\" width=500 height=123 /></span><br><br><strong> ◦ Resources management</strong><br>In Kings&Cities, resources are represented by gauges. Make your choices wisely, because if one of them falls to 0, it is the end of your leadership on Epeiros. <br><br><strong> ◦ Leader's quests</strong><br>During your games, the ruler of your kingdom will send you quests. Complete them to obtain favors.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848390/extras/d0a5d08e8586337d8cb484ccbe93fd8d.poster.avif?t=1694457814\" width=500 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848390/extras/d0a5d08e8586337d8cb484ccbe93fd8d.webm?t=1694457814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1848390/extras/d0a5d08e8586337d8cb484ccbe93fd8d.mp4?t=1694457814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong> ◦ Diplomacy</strong><br>Relations with other kingdoms and empires fluctuate depending on your actions. Find powerful allies to help you but beware! Times are hard and betrayals are common.<br><br><strong> ◦ Cultures & Religions</strong><br>The factions of Kings&Cities are separated into 5 cultures and 6 religions offering great replayability.",
